	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=293317"><span id="Scholar">Poekim</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">70 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>This one took me forever. Finaly got it off a Rockhopper. The thing about this zone is in the caves there are two sets of mobs, the Sambatas and the Rockhoppers. The sambatas are crap they dont frop anything worth havening. The rockhoppers drop hides that can be worth some plat in the bazaar. If the Rockhoppers are up dont kill the Age Old Rockhopper, this will de-spawn them and bring on the Sambatas, you dont want that. If the Sambatas are up use track ( if you got it) find the Sambata Leader and kill him, this will de-spawn them and bring on the rockhoppers. Every thing is green to a 65 so if you gotta be there you might as well kill rockhoppers and get the hides. Good luck</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Poekim <br/>34 Fury 50 Tailor<br/>Butcherblock&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Traders Guild&gt;<br/><br/></td></tr>
